  "uuid": "65ef3b3f2fc7f63d98f60a1f0e9cf86a",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Brand Experience Rep",
  "description": "<h2>🚀 About Vision Organisation</h2><p>Vision Organisation is a people-focused sales & marketing firm that works with leading brands to create memorable, face-to-face experiences.<br />We believe growth happens through real conversations, real teamwork, and real learning on the ground.</p><h2>🎯 Role Overview</h2><p>In this role, you’ll bring brands to life by engaging customers face-to-face at events, campaigns, and outreach activities.<br />Along the way, you’ll build confidence, communication skills, and practical sales experience in a supportive, team-driven environment.</p><h2>🔥 What You’ll Be Doing</h2><ul><li><p>👋 Chat with customers through friendly, professional face-to-face interactions</p></li><li><p>🎤 Represent client brands clearly and confidently at events and campaigns</p></li><li><p>💬 Create positive brand experiences and build genuine connections</p></li><li><p>📈 Develop communication and sales skills through hands-on learning</p></li><li><p>🤝 Work closely with teammates to support campaign goals and deliver consistent messaging</p></li><li><p>⚡ Adapt and grow in a fast-paced, people-focused environment</p></li></ul><h2>🌟 What You’ll Get</h2><ul><li><p>🎓 Structured training provided — no prior experience needed</p></li><li><p>📈 Performance-based growth with clear development pathways</p></li><li><p>🌍 Opportunities to be involved in different campaigns and locations</p></li><li><p>🤝 Supportive mentorship, teamwork, and continuous learning</p></li></ul><h2>🙌 This Role Is Great For You If You</h2><ul><li><p>Enjoy meeting and talking to new people</p></li><li><p>Are motivated, reliable, and open to learning</p></li><li><p>Like active, on-the-ground work (not desk-based)</p></li><li><p>Thrive in energetic, fast-moving environments</p></li></ul><h2>📩 How to Apply</h2><p>Interested in gaining real-world experience in customer engagement and brand representation?<br />We’d love to hear from you.</p><p>📱 <strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 9820 2507<br />💬 <strong>Telegram:</strong> @nitsualim</p>",
